Stanley Quencher H2.0 Soft Matte Collection Stainless Steel Vacuum Insulated Tumbler with Lid and Straw for Iced and Cold Beverages Stormy Sea Soft Matte 40 OZ / 1.18 L
Description: The Quencher H2.0 FlowState™ Tumbler keeps 40 ounces cold for hours thanks to double-wall vacuum insultation. Your go-to tumbler for kicking things off with a rooftop party or gathering to tell tales by the fire—this one is here for it all. The advanced FlowState™ 3-Position Lid has a rotating cover with three versatile positions: a straw opening designed to resist splashes while holding the reusable straw in place a drinking option and a full-cover top. This Quencher even fits in your car cup holder and the easy-grab handle is perfect to bring along for wherever the seasons take you.
